OL,3,CScottish school kids hailed by fire
OL,4,Cchief as they receive bravery award
OL,6,FThree 12-year-olds from the Scottish
OL,7,FBorders have been recognised for their
OL,8,Fbravery after saving a man from a
OL,9,Fhouse fire.
OL,11,FDrae Martin, Teagan Ramsay and Melissa
OL,12,FWatson have all been awarded the
OL,13,FScottish Fire and Rescue Service Chief
OL,14,FOfficer's Commendation.
OL,16,FThe trio raised the alarm as they were
OL,17,Fwalking past a block of flats in in
OL,18,FOctober.
