OL,3,CScottish school kids hailed by fire
OL,4,Cchief as they receive bravery award
OL,6,FThey had heard the smoke alarm coming
OL,7,Ffrom a property where there was a fire
OL,8,Fdeveloping.
OL,10,FDrae, Teagan and Melissa went into the
OL,11,Fstairwell to investigate and tried to
OL,12,Falert the person living in the flat.
OL,14,FThey could not make contact with the
OL,15,Fperson so got a neighbour to call 999
OL,16,Fand they waited for the fire service
OL,17,Fto arrive.
