OL,3,CScottish school kids hailed by fire
OL,4,Cchief as they receive bravery award
OL,6,FChief Officer for Scottish Fire and
OL,7,FRescue Service Ross Haggart said: "I
OL,8,Fwas delighted to present these three
OL,9,Fyoung people with the highest honour
OL,10,Fwe can bestow on a member of the
OL,11,Fpublic. Their quick decision making
OL,12,Fand actions almost certainly saved a
OL,13,Flife on that day.
