OL,3,CScottish school kids hailed by fire
OL,4,Cchief as they receive bravery award
OL,6,F"After they raised the alarm, fire
OL,7,Fservice crews were able to contain the
OL,8,Ffire and ensure the safety of not only
OL,9,Fthe person in the flat, but the rest
OL,10,Fof the building. This was a life and
OL,11,Fdeath situation, and the three
OL,12,Fchildren are true heroes. They richly
OL,13,Fdeserve the award they received.
OL,15,F"Melissa, Teagan and Drae should be
OL,16,Fextremely proud of themselves."
OL,18,FCrews from Galashiels Fire Station
OL,19,Fattended and put the fire out.
