OL,3,CScottish school kids hailed by fire
OL,4,Cchief as they receive bravery award
OL,6,FPaul Gibson, Watch Commander said: "We
OL,7,Ffound a pan of oil on the cooker which
OL,8,Fwas smoking off and boiling over. It
OL,9,Fwas on the verge of catching fire and
OL,10,Fwas probably seconds away from
OL,11,Figniting.
OL,13,F"If they hadn't acted when they did we
OL,14,Fwould have faced a much more serious
OL,15,Fsituation. The fire fighters that were
OL,16,Fin dealing with it would have faced a
OL,17,Fmuch more dangerous and difficult
OL,18,Fscenario.
OL,26,@nD@dOU
