OL,3,CScottish school kids hailed by fire
OL,4,Cchief as they receive bravery award
OL,6,F"The occupier of the building may have
OL,7,Fstruggled to escape, I am pretty sure
OL,8,Fhe would have struggled to escape. The
OL,9,Fother occupants of the block would
OL,10,Fhave been put at risk as well.
OL,12,F"What impressed me about these three
OL,13,Fyoung people is they said to me they
OL,14,Ffelt they had to act because the
OL,15,Fadults who were there and could hear
OL,16,Fthe detector didn't do anything. They
OL,17,Ffelt as though the responsibility was
OL,18,Fon them to do something. That is what
OL,19,Fimpressed me."
