OL,3,CScottish school kids hailed by fire
OL,4,Cchief as they receive bravery award
OL,6,FChris Watson, Melissa's dad said:
OL,7,F"Melissa was meant to be home so we
OL,8,Factually phoned her to see where she
OL,9,Fwas and when she was trying to explain
OL,10,Fwe were about to give her a row then
OL,11,Fwe said we understand.
OL,13,F"We were proud of all three of them
OL,14,Fbecause springing into action and
OL,15,Factually alerting someone and probably
OL,16,Fsaving a life was an immense thing to
OL,17,Fdo for them."
